		<part id="motivation">
			<title>Motivation</title>
			<slide id="apis-and-ai">
				<title>AI needs APIs</title>
				<img src="robot.png" style="float: right ; height : 77% ; margin : 0% 0% 0% 0% ; "/>
				<ol>
					<li>APIs for consumption by AI</li>
					<ul>
						<li><em>GPT Actions</em> provide access to external information sources</li>
						<li><em>MCP provides a plug-in model fo accessing <q>data sources</q></em></li>
					</ul>
					<li>APIs for AI-powered services</li>
					<ul>
						<li>AI tooling for easier creation of applications</li>
						<li>AI applications should become building blocks themselves</li>
					</ul>
					<li>APIs for data ingestion for AI model training</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Data contracts with clear terms of service</li>
					</ul>
				</ol>
			</slide>
			<slide id="scaling-digital">
				<title>APIs &amp; Digital Transformation</title>
				<ul>
					<li>The <q>digital footprint</q> of organizations is growing</li>
					<li>More digital building blocks mean more business options</li>
					<li>Larger organizations have a larger potential to work with</li>
					<li><q>Lift</q> APIs from technical interfaces to business value</li>
					<li>Provide a platform on which APIs are built and consumed</li>
				</ul>
			</slide>
		</part>
