		<part id="success-factors">
			<title>API Platform Success Factors</title>
			<slide id="api-production">
				<title>Factor #1: Supporting API Production</title>
				<ul>
					<li><em>Vision:</em> Everything created has an API</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Essential for automation and AI integration</li>
					</ul>
					<li><em>Strategy:</em> Creating APIs is the default</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Exceptions are possible but need to be justified</li>
					</ul>
					<li><em>Execution:</em> Platform for creating and publishing APIs</li>
					<ul>
						<li><em>API design</em> is automated as much as possible</li>
						<li><em>API chapter</em> as a way to enable all teams</li>
						<li><em>API tooling</em> supports all teams in building/using APIs</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
			</slide>
